    "text": "A wild, jungle road. It's raining heavily. Through the darkness,\nwe can barely make out a convoy of vehicles moving along the road.\nThere are JEEPS, a BULLDOZER, and several large, equipment-laden\nTRUCKS. The convoy moves through the mud toward a large holding\npen. It's surrounded by high fences, alive with electricity and\nblazing lights."
