    "text": "Muldoon and the workers struggle with the gate. An ARM reaches\nout from the darkness inside the box, snatches the WORKER by the\narm and drags him in. His terrified face disappears into the\ndarkness. The SOUND of the raptor is horrible. The other workers\nback away in terror."
